Getwind's purpose is to communicate with a peetbros ultimeter 800 wind station. When the data has
been gathered it is sent to a webserver for presenting the wind/temperature data.

Setup:

Ultimeter 800 ---serial---> MoXA IA240 --ethernet--> 3g router --> internet

A FOSCAM outdoors camera is also connected to the MoXA and pictures are sent to a web server. 

vnstat is included to see that the 1GB limit on the 3g account is not hit

inadyn is used to keep the dynamic host name updated with the 3g routers current ip adress
